{"tid":407435,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"HTC 要賣嗎?? 官方突然宣佈股票暫停交易","createTime":"2017-09-20T12:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T12:06:37.000Z","uid":27240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bbfcaa233d62b79e1985c1f66278ae31479ddd3f","tid":407435,"uid":27240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T12:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/200555_8d9d87243c1c5d2410f5d4486cc33c92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F200555_8d9d87243c1c5d2410f5d4486cc33c92.jpg&h=24da633a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前一直有傳 HTC 將可能出售手機業務的消息 , 而且接洽的對象是 Google . 不過這消息一直都在傳 , 而沒有任何一方出來說個明白 . 但今日傍晚時間 , HTC 突然宣佈 , 明日起(9月21日)暫停股停股票交易 . 難道真的要出售業務了嗎 ?<br />\n<br />\n近日不少經濟新聞都有篇幅報導 HTC 將會在日內就公佈出售手機業務的消息 , 剛巧在這個時間 HTC 突然宣佈股票停牌 . HTC CFO 的呈請中寫明「因有重大訊息待公布，經證交所同意暫停交易日期：106/9/21。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/200536_16e1403998f2c41af2ad841d67059ce0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F200536_16e1403998f2c41af2ad841d67059ce0.jpg&h=6a651019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n估計停牌最大的可能就是 HTC 出售業務 , 因為如果是戰略合作注資一般不需要停牌 , 估計明日或後日就有消息公佈 . 曾經的台灣之光將會迎來什麼樣的狀況 , 估計大家都好緊張 .<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文 : <a href=\"https://qooah.com/2017/09/20/htc-stock-suspension/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2Fhtc-stock-suspension%2F&d=%2Fb725qUfKpa4Zp6WvmEJvrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=22150419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2017/09/20/htc-stock-suspension/</a><br />\n<br />\n跟蹤 <a href=\"http://Qooah.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FQooah.com&d=%2Fb725qUfKpa4Zp6WvmEJvrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=c8ef240a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Qooah.com</a> Facebook 專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/qoooah\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?